00:22:53.660 --> 00:22:55.250
whether it's from
organic traffic

00:22:55.250 --> 00:22:57.730
or whether it's
from paid traffic.

00:22:57.730 --> 00:23:02.130
The tools that you can leverage
so that your game is more

00:23:02.130 --> 00:23:02.730
engaging.

00:23:02.730 --> 00:23:07.210
And last but not
